## Context
This monorepo has:

- `edgework/api`: A Ruby on Rails API exposing RESTful endpoints for authentication, artworks, cart items, orders, and admin content.
- `edgework/web`: A React + Next.js 15 frontend styled with Tailwind CSS.
- JWT authentication stored in localStorage.
- Admin and customer roles, each with separate capabilities.
- Cursor is expected to wire up endpoints and build components that match available backend functionality.
